The script creates a server that can receive commands via UDP and handle file transfers via TCP. It integrates various Raspberry Pi peripherals and capabilities including:

Camera control (single/continuous capture, video recording)

Audio recording and playback

GPIO/LED control

Serial communication

HDMI video output

File transfers

System time setting

OLED display control



